name: A Gift They Will Love!
description:
Linda Roberts is an internationally renowned artist who has been commissioned by the U.S. Ski & Snowboard Team to create original watercolors of gold medal skiers. This winter season Linda is offering to paint a limited number of custom ski paintings! 

Provide a photograph of your loved ones skiing and Linda will paint an original watercolor for you to give to that special person or couple this year. And, if you'd like to share this gift with more friends or family members, contact us about having prints or note cards made from the original!

TO ORDER
Please email Linda through our CONTACT page on the menu above to receive instructions for forwarding a photograph of your loved ones skiing or snowboarding (Linda prefers that pictures are mailed due to monitor color variation but an emailed photo is also acceptable).  

Click "ADD TO CART" and proceed with checkout.

QUESTIONS?
Please visit the CONTACT page on our menu above and email Linda with any questions you have.

HOLIDAY DELIVERY
Because delivery services are busy during the holidays Linda is offering to provide a special gift card free of charge that can be given to people to let them know they will be receiving a Linda Roberts’ original painting with the New Year. The card will include picture hangers so that you may insert a copy of the photograph you selected. Please let us know if you would like this service when placing your order.

SHIPPING
We will ship your order 10 to 14 days after the date we receive your photograph. You will be notified via email when we have your photo in hand.

Packages will be mailed standard USPS unless expedited shipping is requested at time of order.  Standard USPS shipping cost is a flat rate of $20.00. Expedited shipping cost will be calculated and emailed to you prior to shipment.

USER AGREEMENT
Linda looks forward to painting your loved ones skiing! By placing your custom painting order through this website you confirm that you have read the terms and conditions, that you understand them, and that you agree to be bound by them.

TERMS & CONDITIONS
Your custom painting will reflect Linda's general style as reflected in her paintings on this website.  Your original watercolor painting will not be an exact replicate of your photograph; colors and details may vary.  Additionally, Linda prefers to paint a side or rear view of skiers, rather than a frontal view.
